Support these block patterns:

 - `[‌[‌url‌]‌]` → `http://127.0.0.1/a`
 - `[‌[‌url.scheme]‌]` → `http`
 - `[‌[‌url.protocol‌]‌]` → `http://`
 - `[‌[‌url.host‌]‌]` → `127.0.0.1`
 - `[‌[‌url.port‌]‌]` → `80`
 - `[‌[‌url.directory‌]‌]` → `/a`
 - `[‌[‌url.i‌]‌]` → `1`
 - `[‌[‌url.path‌]‌]` → `/foo/bar`
 - `[‌[‌url.query‌]‌]` → `?foo=bar&baz=qux`
 - `[‌[‌url.clean‌]‌]` → `http://127.0.0.1/a/foo/bar`
 - `[‌[‌url.current‌]‌]` → `http://127.0.0.1/a/foo/bar/1`